Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.52,0:23:34.78,Default,,0,0,20,,How are you feeling? I am Benio
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.03,0:23:41.57,Default,,0,0,20,,Please call me High Collar Lady, \Nbecause I'm in that phase
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.49,0:23:48.50,Default,,0,0,20,,When it's getting so hard \Nto be honest with the people I love
