Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.78,0:01:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The wandering dejected flower \Nblooms wildly in her drunken frenzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.13,0:01:25.67,Default,,0,0,0,,In his search for her, Shinobu checks out every public disturbance in the city.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.67,0:01:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Meanwhile, Ushigorou hurries to the Count for reinforcements,{一方ushigorouは援軍を迎えに伊集院伯爵家に走ったが}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,only for him to cause even more trouble!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.29,0:01:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Lieutenant Colonel​?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.27,0:01:43.08,Default,,0,0,0,,That geezer is out of his mind!{大変な爺さんにうちあがった}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.52,0:01:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,When Shinobu finally arrives, \Nhis jubilation is short-lived,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.84,0:01:53.97,Default,,0,0,0,,as the opponent happens to be none other than Shinobu's direct superior, now deeply aggrieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.97,0:01:57.89,Default,,0,0,0,,This might just be the beginning \Nof an endless tragedy.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.97,0:02:03.90,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,300)\c&HF4F3FD&\bord0\b1\blur1.001\pos(719,229)}Episode 19\N{\fs130}Fleeting Happiness {つかの間の幸せ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.29,0:02:07.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.68,0:02:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Uhm... Uhm, you haven't paid your bill yet.{あのあのまだお勘定頂いてないんですけども}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:16.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, pay her.{払っとけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.97,0:02:18.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure, but...{あ、しかし}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.46,0:02:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Just shut up and pay!{払えって言ったら払っとけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.89,0:02:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Right...\NSo how much is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.84,0:02:24.87,Default,,0,0,0,,3 yen 50 sen, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.87,0:02:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,There!{ほら}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.58,0:02:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Much obliged!{ありがとうございました}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.23,0:02:30.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Running with your tail between your legs?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.14,0:02:31.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.06,0:02:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, don't forget your things!{はい、これ忘れ物よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.40,0:02:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you treat a soldier's soul like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.34,0:02:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You call that a soul? \NGimme that, Ranko.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.62,0:02:45.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Only a katana is fit to contain the warrior's soul!\NTake a look! {/japanese sword (as opposed to a saber)}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.53,0:02:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,My precious saber!{わしの大事なサーべルを}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.34,0:02:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,If that tin scrap is what our soldiers consider their soul, \Nthe future isn't looking bright for the Japanese Army,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.51,0:03:00.72,Default,,0,0,0,,imbecile!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.32,0:03:04.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I tried to act respectfully, \Non account of your age...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.87,0:03:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Asking for more?{まだやるか}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.58,0:03:10.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You forgot something else.{あら、もう一つ忘れ物よ}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.71,0:03:12.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Another piece of your soul.{大事な魂}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.12,0:03:15.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.48,0:03:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.49,0:03:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,You brat...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.82,0:03:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Lt. Col?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.57,0:03:26.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.16,0:03:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll regret making fun of the army!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.25,0:03:33.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Weirdo!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.45,0:03:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Tsk! Hey, we're out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.49,0:03:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That wasn't half-bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.06,0:03:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, let's go home too.{さ、我々も帰ろう}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.01,0:03:49.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a triumphant return!{凱旋じゃあ凱旋じゃあ}\NHip hip, hooray!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.48,0:03:52.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Geez, Count, you truly are something else!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.40,0:03:55.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I guess we should be on our way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.28,0:03:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.49,0:03:59.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, whoops. Oh, eh?{ええ……お、おっと、あら、あら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:08.13,Default,,0,0,0,,What's happening to me?{わらしどうしたのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.62,0:04:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{unimportant}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.72,0:04:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:24.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that the fight's over, \Nit seems the alcohol has kicked in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.30,0:04:26.89,Default,,0,0,0,,How embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.37,0:04:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,One, two, and three!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.14,0:04:36.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:38.05,Default,,0,0,0,,T-The Earth is spinning too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:43.47,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H2223D9&\3c&H75DCF0&\fs120\blur1.001\b1}Bam! {idk really what sound to make of it, some slam?}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.82,0:04:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,How about we return like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.92,0:04:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm shocked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.71,0:04:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No way!{だめです}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.75,0:04:56.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you see how embarrassing this is?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:05:00.48,Default,,0,0,0,,It's just a husband carrying his wife on his back. \NWhat's so embarrassing about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.48,0:05:02.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Wife?!{\i0} Wife... He said wife...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Wife?! Wife! Wife? \NNever! Never! Put me down! Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.99,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Ahem!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.43,0:05:11.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down! Put me down! Down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:11.82,Overlap,,0,0,0,,I think it's only fair that a husband should pay her bill. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.86,0:05:12.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.36,0:05:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Won't you look for a moment \Nat what she's done!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:20.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Five chairs, three desks, decanters, \Nglasses and plates,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:23.03,Default,,0,0,0,,for a total of... A total of...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.03,0:05:23.03,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Never! Never! Let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.57,0:05:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I apologise, we'll compensate you for everything.{すいませんすべて弁償しますから}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.36,0:05:26.43,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Just let go of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.43,0:05:31.11,Default,,0,0,0,,She ain't getting no compensation!\NWhy should we pay her for any of that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll hurt yourself if you keep struggling like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.11,0:05:34.04,Overlap,,0,0,0,,Let go of me! Put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.04,0:05:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Shut up! Shut it, you all!{うるさい　うるさい}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.80,0:05:37.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.80,0:05:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.81,0:05:42.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you alright, Benio?{大丈夫ですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.32,0:05:46.13,Default,,0,0,0,,And one pillar too.{それに柱一本}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.13,0:05:47.72,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&HD3D8D6&\3c&H316A75&\fs100\bord1\pos(1139,346)}Puff {idk what to make of this sound effect as well, would surmise some sound of soul leaving the body or such}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.34,0:05:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,A messenger came from the mountain village...{花咲かば　告げんといひし　山里の}{https://manyuraku.exblog.jp/24288183/}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.31,0:06:00.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He came from the mountain village riding a horse...{告げんといひし　山里の}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.25,0:06:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,To tell everyone that the cherries had blossomed...{使いは来たり　馬に鞍}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.37,0:06:10.57,Default,,0,0,0,,The double cherry blossoms on the Kurama Mountain...{鞍馬の山の　うづ桜}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.12,0:06:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Count's looking pretty merry. \NWhat is that chant, though?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.04,0:06:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,The Kurama Tengu Noh song.{謡曲鞍馬天狗}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.79,0:06:19.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you so gloomy then, Ranbuddy?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.07,0:06:20.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a guess...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.26,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It feels like this exact same thing \Nalready happened once a long time ago...{ずーっと昔これとそっくり同じことがあっ たみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.30,0:06:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Being carried on someone's broad and steady back...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.22,0:06:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Was that... my father?{あれはお父様}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.15,0:06:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,No...\NNo, not him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.65,0:06:48.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It wasn't my father.{お父様ではない}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.57,0:06:52.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it... Was it someone I don't know?{誰か誰か知らない人}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.58,0:06:57.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I was fated to be carried on someone's strong back...{私はそのたくましい人に負ぶさる運命だった}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.79,0:07:01.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It was decided from the very beginning.{ずっと昔からその運命は決まっていった}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.15,0:07:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,But who...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.49,0:07:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was supposed to be that man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.59,0:07:42.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I slept so well!{よく寝た}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.71,0:07:51.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.87,0:07:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Dazzling!{眩しい}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.75,0:07:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.{おはようございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.08,0:07:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, good m-
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.58,0:07:59.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you awake already, Lady Benio?{もうお目覚めでございますか紅緒様}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.16,0:08:02.04,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that supposed to mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.56,0:08:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,How in the world did I return here?{私この家に帰ってきちゃったんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.96,0:08:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,You're welcome to live here again \Nfrom today onwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.02,0:08:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.00,0:08:09.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow-ow-ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.12,0:08:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this? Did I hit my head?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.66,0:08:19.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! Where did this giant bump come from? \NAnd when did I get it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.57,0:08:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Can't you remember?{覚えてないんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.45,0:08:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Sh-Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.88,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Morning. Feeling better already?{おはよう御機嫌いかがですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.09,0:08:31.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What happened yesterday was so like you!{昨日のこと 全く紅緒さんらしいな}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.80,0:08:39.08,Default,,0,0,0,,By the way, when did I get this bump?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.08,0:08:41.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You really can't recall?{本当に覚えがないんですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.58,0:08:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I came back home, I quarreled with my father,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.28,0:08:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,then me, Ushigorou and Ranmaru went to get just a bit of alcohol...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.94,0:08:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a {\i1}bit{\i0} of alcohol?{お酒をちょっぴり}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.57,0:08:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That's as far as I can remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.35,0:08:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But everything after that...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.06,0:08:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,has slipped my memory entirely!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.67,0:09:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny? \NAre you that fond of laughing at others' worries?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.99,0:09:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. I'm s-sorry, \Nbut this is also so much like you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.55,0:09:16.39,Default,,0,0,0,,How about here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.39,0:09:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It hurts! Be gentler!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.68,0:09:23.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't I say you would sprain your back again if you pushed yourself so hard at this age?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What's so funny?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:28.84,Default,,0,0,0,,If only you saw my heroism last night!{何を申す？昨夜の大活躍見せたかったぞ！}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I knocked out every soldier, one after another,\Nso it's no wonder they took flight in the end.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.82,0:09:38.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.67,0:09:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you listening to what I'm saying at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.68,0:09:41.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.17,0:09:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget it. Just come here and look at this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.50,0:09:49.99,Default,,0,0,0,,There'd better be a good reason \Nwhy you stopped massaging me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.05,0:09:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, isn't it a sight for sore eyes, dear?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.00,0:09:59.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Right, Tenmaru and Chimaru look really healthy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.01,0:10:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Not the dogs!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But...{しかし}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.85,0:10:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio is finally back to how she was before. {to bury the hatchet; to make up; to be reconciled; to be reunited (e.g. couple);}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.01,0:10:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. This is also only thanks to my heroic fighting against eight enemies at once last night!{これも全て昨夜わしが8人突起の大活躍をしたなれば こそじゃ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.03,0:10:20.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Is blowing hot air about your bravery \Nthe only thing you can think of?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.27,0:10:26.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Those two are making the new flowers \Nbloom in this old mansion.{あの人たちはこの古い家に新しい花を咲かせてくれるのですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.96,0:10:29.19,Default,,0,0,0,,If they have children at some point,{二人の間に子供が生まれるば}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.19,0:10:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,those will be our great-grandchildren.{それは私たちのひ孫になるのですよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.38,0:10:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I know that! You all think of me as boorish,\Nbut even I can appreciate such simple beauty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.57,0:10:40.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Not my fault I'm bad at expressing emotions!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.55,0:10:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I wish nothing but happiness \Nfor those two, as much as everyone else.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.56,0:10:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Still... If I was that drunk,\Nhow on earth did I make it back here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.78,0:10:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.15,0:10:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Did I come here on Ushigorou's rickshaw?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.16,0:10:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Probably... Maybe.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.93,0:10:57.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.24,0:11:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm dead sure someone carried me on his back.{違うわ私は 確か負ぶさって帰ってきたんだわ}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.54,0:11:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Who was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.45,0:11:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.40,0:11:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I think...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.79,0:11:07.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! I've remembered!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.91,0:11:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,So who carried you on his back?{誰に背負われたんです}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.13,0:11:13.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I know! That all happened in my dream only.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.36,0:11:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,In reality, I got home on my own.{本当は誰にも負ぶされなかった}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.85,0:11:31.03,Default,,0,0,0,,My love that I thought lost will finally bear fruit two generations later, in our grandson Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.70,0:11:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Shinobu...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.21,0:11:34.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.91,0:11:37.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be happy together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.20,0:11:41.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever hurdles you may face in life, \Nyou'll overcome them with ease.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.08,0:11:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,You know, that got me so worked up! And...{no clue what this is about}{/panicked/startled/hurried}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.49,0:12:05.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright. This is the perfect time \Nto tell her my feelings.{そうだ今日こそ僕の心を紅緒さんに行って しまおう}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.32,0:12:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Here, I think it suits you.{はい、綺麗でしょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.97,0:12:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Benio.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:13.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.23,0:12:16.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Why the serious tone?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.02,0:12:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something... \NI've always wanted to tell you.{あなたに話そうと考えていたことがあるのです}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.44,0:12:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You see, I...{僕は}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.40,0:12:26.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shinobu!\NLook there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.41,0:12:38.35,Default,,0,0,0,,What a rare sight! \NThe cockroaches are flying in a flock!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.09,0:12:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoa! They're a single line now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.55,0:12:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? It's V-shaped now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.31,0:12:46.98,Default,,0,0,0,,So? Isn't that peculiar?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.98,0:12:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, by the way, what did you want to tell me?{ところで何の話でしたっけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.02,0:12:55.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no, is something wrong?{あらやだどうかなさったの}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.26,0:12:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you feeling unwell?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.19,0:12:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, talk to me.{ねぇ少尉ったら}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.56,0:13:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I'm fine.\NIt can wait for a better day.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.53,0:13:02.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But...{でも}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.44,0:13:06.43,Default,,0,0,0,,The mood needs to be just right \Nfor that kind of conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I need to leave soon.{僕そろそろ出かけなければ}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.13,0:13:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,See you in the evening, Benio.{じゃあまたね}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.00,0:13:12.81,Default,,0,0,0,,A-Ah... Sh-Shinobu!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.79,0:13:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,What a weirdo.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.00,0:13:20.59,Default,,0,0,0,,He could've just said it then and there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.09,0:13:23.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, that guy doesn't know what he wants himself. {/he ruined the tempo}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.97,0:13:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh God! R-Ranmaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.44,0:13:39.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.82,0:13:42.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What does it look like? \NI'm working out.{視ればわかるでしょう体を鍛えてるの }
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.82,0:13:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? But are you sure it's safe \Nfor your delicate fingers?{だってそんなことしたらあんたの大事な白魚の指が}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.53,0:13:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, Benio.{安心してよbenio-san}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.24,0:13:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be the one protecting you, \Nwithout relying on that lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.57,0:14:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I just don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.95,0:14:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Something must've happened last night, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.80,0:14:07.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning, Lady Benio!{おはようございます}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.94,0:14:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, morning!{おはようよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.72,0:14:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what do you think this voice is?{なんだ、何かしらの声}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.67,0:14:14.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds like Ranko.{蘭子さんみたい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.90,0:14:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh! Oh shoot!{やばい}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.43,0:14:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What could she be doing?{何してるのかしら}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.02,0:14:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go see!{行ってみましょうよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.08,0:14:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.28,0:14:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hold on!\NN-No! You can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.57,0:14:25.66,Default,,0,0,0,,H-How come?{どうしてですか}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.66,0:14:28.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, well, you see... \NShe's there, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.55,0:14:32.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Ranko is one of us, so it's fine, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.10,0:14:32.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.78,0:14:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Sounds about right. {\i1}Right?{\i0}{そうですかわ、ねえ}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.94,0:14:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Beg your pardon!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.27,0:14:40.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I've done what I could...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.85,0:15:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What's up, girls?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.92,0:15:06.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Weren't you making strange sounds here just now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.52,0:15:08.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah. I was just exercising, you see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.90,0:15:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Exercising?{ 体操}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.15,0:15:11.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, doing calisthenics.{そう 美容体操}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.76,0:15:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, so it was calisthenics?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.33,0:15:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Wonderful!\NI also want to be as fit and pretty as Ranko!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.90,0:15:19.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Take me with you tomorrow, will you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.87,0:15:22.36,Default,,0,0,0,,And me! Please!\N{\i1}Won't you, Ranko?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.36,0:15:23.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach us how to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.54,0:15:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Teach us, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.17,0:15:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, you girls... \NFine, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.31,0:15:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yay! Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.16,0:15:33.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, shall we go now?{じゃ行きましょう}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.18,0:15:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank God! \NHe was this close to getting exposed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.53,0:15:51.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I'll be on my way, Benio.{では行ってくるよBenioさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.15,0:15:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Come home safe!{いってらっしゃい}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.82,0:16:00.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Come home safe,{\i0} Young Master.{いってらっしゃいませ若様}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.84,0:16:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.17,0:16:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So, Boss, we should also get going \Nin a couple of minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.90,0:16:15.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? Where to?{どこへ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.05,0:16:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,No way you really are that forgetful!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.76,0:16:20.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to skip school?{学校サボるんでやんすかい}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,C'mon, get on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.52,0:16:25.43,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H191A1F&\3c&HDADDDF&\b1\blur1.001\fax-0.005233\fscx90.20\fscy129.96\frz-9.6926\frx-7.0458\fry2.3500\xbord3.68\ybord5.20\org(734.93,288.62)\pos(735.05,256.13)}Boss Benio's ride {I don't really remember how I tled this last time}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.43,0:16:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still a school student, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.61,0:16:28.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! You're right...{そうだっけ}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.54,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's been so much stuff happening lately, \Nthat I've forgotten completely about school!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.97,0:16:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean you've not done \Na smidgen of homework either?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.76,0:16:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Naturally!{もちろん}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.67,0:16:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, I guess, maybe you should play hooky just today, after all?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.60,0:16:42.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Deal!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.44,0:16:46.17,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the first smart thing you've said \Never since I met you!{あんた私と知り合って初めていいことを言ったわね}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.17,0:16:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Like boss, like underling, they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.72,0:16:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, I'll just go to town \Nto attend to some business.{出しゃれ街へ出てちょいとしとか席}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.16,0:16:54.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Here we go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.60,0:16:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then, don't miss me, Boss! {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.81,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck with your business!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.78,0:17:10.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ijuuin... Oh, so it's here?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.28,0:17:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,That's one luxurious manor. \NMeans I'll have no problem collecting the dues!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.54,0:17:22.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.59,0:17:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm a decent woman, \Nyou've no reason to suspect me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.13,0:17:31.36,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Somebody help me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.99,0:17:35.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Rickshaw, help me!{車屋さん助けて}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.97,0:17:38.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Aren't you last night's proprietress?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.82,0:17:44.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes I am, and I'm here to bill Mr. Second Lieutenant \Nfor yesterday's damages!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.49,0:17:45.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Tough luck, then. {no clue}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.45,0:17:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You! Please do something about these dogs. \NI'm begging you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.65,0:17:55.18,Default,,0,0,0,,No can do. \NThese two are my eternal nemeses.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.18,0:18:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Proprietress, I don't mean to be rude, but if you value your life, you'd better give up and turn back now.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.60,0:18:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Did they want to threaten me? {guess}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.48,0:18:07.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you've only got one life, \Nso don't waste it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:09.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.28,0:18:15.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you kidding me?\NI {\i1}need{\i0} to do this to make ends meet!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.21,0:18:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, then! \NIf I can't get it here, I'll get it elsewhere! {いいよいいよここがダメならあっちがあるんだhttps://youtu.be/GA3uDD66byI}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.38,0:18:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.75,0:18:31.15,Default,,0,0,0,,You cannot come through.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.15,0:18:33.43,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I just wanted to ask for a favor.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.43,0:18:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what does that civilian want?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.36,0:18:40.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, you see, I'd like you \Nto give this to Second Lieutenant Ijuuin.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.84,0:18:48.57,Default,,0,0,0,,It's open, come in.{よし、入れ}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.88,0:18:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer on guard duty here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.80,0:18:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,At ease. What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.77,0:18:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,We just had a civilian, \Nwho asked us to deliver this to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.07,0:19:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, really? She came all the way here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.64,0:19:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I got it. Please tell the giver \Nthat I'll be sure to pay it in full.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.04,0:19:09.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir. That's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.10,0:19:24.48,Default,,0,0,0,,This one is done.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.14,0:19:28.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Officer on duty here! {could make "assistant/adjutant/etc"}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.36,0:19:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I need a favor from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.92,0:19:33.64,Default,,0,0,0,,These documents on the desk,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.64,0:19:36.12,Default,,0,0,0,,could you deliver them to\NLt. Col Innen at headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.12,0:19:38.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir! Understood!{わかりました}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.72,0:19:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I shall now go deliver this \Nto Lieutenant Colonel​ Innen!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.07,0:19:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,If you'll excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.11,0:19:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, thanks.{あ、頼んだよ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Attention! {/ten-hut}\NSalute!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.14,0:20:09.64,Sign,,0,0,0,,{\c&H231A0F&\3c&H538080&\fax-0.368963\fscx77.34\fscy167.99\frz-0.4089\frx9.6415\fry2.2366\xbord3.16\ybord6.72\org(599.03,1021.27)\pos(606.16,979.27)}Main Administrative Office {本部事務室 - not sure what to make of it, seems to be very serious house of officialdom where they handle a lot of papers}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.37,0:20:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So infuriating...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.29,0:20:18.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That hoyden is Hanamura's daughter...{花村の娘とは言っとったのやつ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.26,0:20:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! Just thinking about her irritates me!{思い出しても腹の立つ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.53,0:20:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you need me for something, Lieutenant Colonel​?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.75,0:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh? N-No, it's nothing.{いやべつに}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.{そうなんだ}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.44,0:20:36.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Major Hanamura.{やぁ花札さん}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.19,0:20:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Correspondence for you from Second Lieutenant\NIjuuin of 1st Battalion, 3rd Company!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.15,0:20:42.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What? From Second Lieutenant Ijuuin?{何 伊集院少尉}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.03,0:20:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Yessir, he asked me to give you this.{はこれをお届けするようにと}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.03,0:20:48.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you. Dismissed.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.66,0:20:51.34,Default,,0,0,0,,That Ijuuin again...{伊集院め}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.34,0:20:55.17,Default,,0,0,0,,He, who ignores our regulations against long hair in broad daylight...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,And he's not even a pure Japanese.{おまけに純生の日本人でもないくせに}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't stand the fact that someone like him \Nis a part of the sacred Imperial Army.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.60,0:21:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,I need to give him tit for tat, \None way or another.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.06,0:21:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.29,0:21:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,A compensation for five stools, three desks, \Ndecanters, glasses and plates?{椅子五個、机三、ちょうしとコップと皿の弁償金}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.60,0:21:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this scrap?\NAn invoice from last night's tavern?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.41,0:21:21.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ugh! That Ijuuin again...{もう伊集院め}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.42,0:21:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Did he forward it to me, \Nimplying I should pay for that too?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.70,0:21:27.14,Default,,0,0,0,,That was the last straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.37,0:21:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,This is just unacceptable!{断じているせん}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.05,0:21:35.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Scary, scary! That was the line one ought not to cross with Lieutenant Colonel Innen!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.13,0:21:37.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, the intervention in Russia?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.03,0:21:44.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. We might need to dispatch some of our troops \Nto Siberia alongside Americans.{我が軍もアメリカと共にシベリアへ出兵することになるかもしれん}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.39,0:21:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Would be a good show of force.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.09,0:21:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,The year is 1918 and Japan is about to dispatch \Nan expeditionary corps to Siberia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.64,0:21:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Intervention in Russia, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.64,0:21:56.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This could prove expedient.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.98,0:22:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,There. Aren't they pretty,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.03,0:22:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,my lieutenant?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.25,0:22:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,The gentle breeze of love \Nsuddenly turns into a violent typhoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.73,0:22:34.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Will it be enough to blow High Collar Lady's happiness completely away?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.00,0:22:39.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Was this happiness just a fleeting dream?{幸せは 束の間の儚い夢なのか}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.60,0:22:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in danger!{危うし}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.95,0:22:43.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in danger, High Collar Lady!{危うしはいからさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.37,0:22:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Our High Collar Lady now trusts Shinobu, not caring about his mountain of love letters,{少尉を信じるハイカラさんは\N山のラブレター気にもせず}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.00,0:23:01.03,Default,,0,0,0,,and she decides to go shopping in Gofukubashi.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.03,0:23:07.01,Default,,0,0,0,,However, to her horror, she stumbles \Nacross Shinobu, who's on a date
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.01,0:23:10.06,Default,,0,0,0,,with none other than the beautiful geisha Kichiji.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.06,0:23:11.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do now?{さてどうする}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.61,0:23:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you gonna do, High Collar Lady?{どうするするハイカラさん}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.69,0:23:15.56,Default,,0,0,0,,See in the next episode of {\i1}Here Comes the High Collar Lady:{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.56,0:23:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,"Who Are Those Two Under \Nthe Love Umbrella?"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.49,0:23:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't miss it!{相合傘のお二人はお楽しみに}
